If they own the rights only for US, what about finding a distributor in Europe, expecially France? After having seen the success of Sita in Berlin and Annecy, where usually also distributors come, I guess some arthouse distributor in France could take the film into consideration.<br />
Of course, if the big music companies own the rights worldwide, forget all what I said.</p>
